channel.title: Help changing floor tiles and hills
channel.description: I am trying to clear the fountain area from ::fish and I want to change the floor texture and get rid of bumps and make it even. I haven't found a tut for this yet so I was hoping someone knows how. If you help me completely design this area for my server, I will make you the new mod of my server.[br][size=1]Posted at: November 07, 2006, 06:26:33 PM[/size][hr]come on.... please someone?[br][size=1]Posted at: November 07, 2006, 07:23:20 PM[/size][hr]Wow.... Im on a forum with some of the worlds top Javascript coders and they cant even tell me how to edit a frikin floor tile.... Sad...
